    public interface IService
    A Service is any object that provides some form of service. Services can be configured and are accessible to all components in Catalys via look up from the ServiceRegistry.

    Some examples of services are:

    • a market mirror - a service that keeps track of the state of orders in a market.
    • a market data service.
